</ref> They were nominated for Best African Group at the 2017 Afrimma Awards.\n\n==History==\nThe group was formed in 2009. The members of Best Life Music shared a passion for [[Hip hop music|hip-hop]]. After the local success of their single \"Ma Lova\" which caused a stir on the [[Burundian music]] scene in 2015, and along with other songs like \"Better Than\",<ref>{{cite news|title=Best Life Music \u2013 Better Than (Burundi)|url=http://www.bongo5.com/new-music-best-life-music-burundi-better-than-06-2015/|accessdate=27 June 2015|agency=Bongo 5|publisher=Bongo 5}}</ref> they became one of the locally favorite artists.<ref>{{cite news|title=Sat-Be: partager la r\u00e9ussite avec les artistes burundais Best Life Music|url=http://www.burundi-eco.com/index.php/art-et-culture/musique/75-sat-be-partager-la-reussite-avec-les-artistes-burundais|accessdate=15 November 2013|publisher=Burundi Eco|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141210194602/http://www.burundi-eco.com/index.php/art-et-culture/musique/75-sat-be-partager-la-reussite-avec-les-artistes-burundais|archive-date=10 December 2014|url-status=dead}}</ref> In 2014 [[Kora Entertainment]] in partnership with the label [[Music of Africa|African]] Sound Records and Best Life Music made a song in collaboration with Congolese singer Dety Darba (Happy People). It has been named the official song of a major annual event of the edition HAPPY PEOPLE 2014. Among their musical activities, Best Life Music made their first video that talks about their [[Musical instrument|musical]] career called ''Who Is Best Life Music?'' which is divided into seasons.\n\n==Musical style==\nTheir music combines elements of [[hip-hop]] and [[African popular music|Afro-pop]]. They rap in English, [[Kirundi]], French and [[Swahili language|Swahili]] to reflect their origins in East Africa.<ref>{{cite web|title=Sikiliza Good Music kutoka BURUNDI, vijana hawa wanaitwa BEST LIFE MUSIC wimbo KENKELEWA|url=http://djchokamusic.com/sikiliza-good-music-kutoka-burundi-vijana-hawa-wanaitwa-best-life-music-wimbo-kenkelewa/|website=djchokamusic.com/|publisher=Dj Choka|accessdate=5 December 2014}}</ref> Best Life Music uses influences from global, African, and local engineering in the creation of their music.\n\n==Current members==\n* Dany Lo<ref>{{cite news|title=Umurundi Young Dany yatatse u Rwanda anatangaza imishinga agiye gukorana n'abahanzi nyarwanda|url=http://smart.inyarwanda.com/articles/show/EntertainmentNews/umurundi-young-dany-yatatse-u-rwanda-anatangaza-imishinga-agiye-gukorana-n-abahanzi-nyarwanda-64309.html|accessdate=6 June 2015|publisher=Inyarwanda.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150623141534/http://smart.inyarwanda.com/articles/show/EntertainmentNews/umurundi-young-dany-yatatse-u-rwanda-anatangaza-imishinga-agiye-gukorana-n-abahanzi-nyarwanda-64309.html|archive-date=23 June 2015|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Young Dany|url=http://www.thebestlifemusic.com/young-dany-photoshoot-mutanga/|website=thebestlifemusic.com/|publisher=BLM|accessdate=7 September 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006205447/http://www.thebestlifemusic.com/young-dany-photoshoot-mutanga/|archive-date=6 October 2014|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Best Life bashigikirana n'inyuma y'umuziki|url=http://indundi.com/news/page/63829/indundi-magazine-best-life-bashigikirana-n-inyuma-y-umuziki|date=25 January 2015|accessdate=2 February 2015|work=Indundi Magazine|author=King Yann Cool|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150203051655/http://indundi.com/news/page/63829/indundi-magazine-best-life-bashigikirana-n-inyuma-y-umuziki|archive-date=3 February 2015|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n* Young Jpy\n* G Kiboko\n* Mc Vitaa\n\n==Discography==\n\n=== Studio albums ===\n* ''Addicted''\n\n=== EP===\n\n;Arrependimento\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"  | Title\n! scope=\"col\"  | Cover\n! scope=\"col\"  | Album details\n! scope=\"col\"  |Notes\n|-\n! 