ww.worldofafrica.tv/videos/best-life-music-ft-patient-matabaro-never-sleep-official-video/|accessdate=15 January 2014|publisher=world of africa}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Never Sleep By Best Life Music Ft Patient Matabaro|url=http://www.greatlakesmix.com/videos/14225/never-sleep-by-best-life-music-ft-patient-matabaro-official-video|publisher=Glm Mix}}</ref> \n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2014\n| Kent-P\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Don't Forget\"\n| Kent-P\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"RayBan\"\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2015\n| Kent-P\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Better Than\"\n| Meddy Saleh\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Ma Lova\"\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2016\n| Kent-P\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Overdose\"\n| Kent-P\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Your Vodo\"\n| rowspan=\"1\"| 2017\n| Kent-P\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Hello\"\n| rowspan=\"1\"| 2018\n| Sasha Vybz\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"NkuyaKuya\" featuring MB Data\n| rowspan=\"1\"| 2019\n| Kent-P\n|-\n|}\n\n==Videos: Who Is Best Life Music?==\n*Season 1 Episode 01 \u2013 Photoshoot\n*Season 1 Episode 02 \u2013 Changamka Show Rema FM with Ismail NIYONKURU \n*Season 1 Episode 03 \u2013 Don't Forget\n*Season 1 Episode 04 \u2013 Nezererwa na SMS media with Eddy Kamoso\n*Season 1 Episode 05 \u2013 Happy BirthDay Brenda\n*Season 1 Episode 06 \u2013 High Girl Studio Session\n*Season 1 Episode 07 \u2013 Behind The Scenes RayBan\n\n==Awards==\n=== African Entertainment Awards USA ===\n{{awards table}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\"|2019\n|Best Life Music\n|Hottest Group\n|{{pending}}\n|-\n{{end}}\n\n===[[Buja Music Awards]]===\n{{awards table}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\"|2019\n|Nkuyakuya\n|Best Collaboration\n|{{Nom}}\n|-\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\"|2019\n|Nkuyakuya\n|Best Music Video\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\"|2019\n|Best Life Music\n|Best Group\n|{{win}}\n|-\n{{end}}\n\n=== AMI Afrika People's Choice Awards ===\n{{awards table}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\"|2018\n|Best Life Music \u2013 Your Vodo (Burundi)\n|Best African Group\n|{{cancelled}}\n|-\n{{end}}\n\n=== Afrimma Awards ===\n{{awards table}}\n|-\