=Junero|last=Lawrence|date=May 4, 2019}}</ref>\n\n=== Categories ===\n*Artist Of The Year\n*Song Of The Year\n*Best Collaboration\n*Best Hip Hop Song\n*Best Hip Hop Artist\n*Best RNB/Afro Song\n*Best Music Duo/Group\n*Best Performance\n*Best Male Artist\n*Best Female Artist\n*Best New Artist\n*Video Of The Year\n*Best Music Producer\n*Best Video Director\n*Best DJ\n*Best Diaspora Artist\n*Best Comedian\n*Best Tradi-Modern Artist/Group\n*Best Dancer Group\n*Best Radio Presenter\n*Best Gospel Artist/ Group\n\n===Nominees===\n2019 nominees & Winners list<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://juliablaise.com/buja-music-awards-2019-unveil-nominees-list/ |title=Archived copy |access-date=2019-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190506095134/https://juliablaise.com/buja-music-awards-2019-unveil-nominees-list/ |archive-date=2019-05-06 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://an24.net/2019/05/06/buja-music-awards-2019-see-full-list-of-nominees/|title=Buja Music Awards 2019: See Full List Of Nominees|first=Ukhueleigbe|last=Zaccheus|date=May 6, 2019}}</ref>\n[[Buja Music Awards 2019]]\n\n{| class=wikitable\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width=50%\" | Artist Of The Year\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width=50%\" | Song Of The Year\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width=50%\" | Best Collaboration\n|-\n| valign=\"Artist Of the year\" |\n*'''[[Sat-B]]'''\n**B Face\n**Lolilo\n**[[Masterland]]\n| valign=\"Song of the year\" |\n*'''No Love by [[Sat-B]]'''\n**Iwawe by Akes Don ft Vichou love\n**Utuntu by Dr Claude\n**Mon Amour by [[Miss Erica]]\n**Guitar by Lolilo\n**Sabwe by [[Masterland]]\n| valign=\"Best Collaboration\" |\n*'''Iwawe by Akes Don ft Vichou love'''\n**Only One by Mt Number One ft [[Sat-B]]\n**NkuyaKuya by [[Best Life Music]] ft MB Data\n**Oloha by Dj Philbyte ft B Face\n**Koroka by El Coyotte ft Dr Claude\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width=50%\" |Best Hip Hop Song\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width=50%\" |Best Hip Hop Artist\n! style=\"backgro