{"title_page": "Arrependimento II", "text_new": "{{Infobox album\n| name       = Arrependimento II\n| type       = studio\n| artist     = [[Best Life Music]]\n| cover      =\n| alt        =\n| released   = {{start date|2016|09|11}}\n| recorded   = 2014\u20132016\n| venue      =\n| studio     =\n| genre      = [[R&B]], [[afrobeat]], [[Afro pop music|afropop]]\n| length     = {{Duration|m=67|s=41}}\n| label      = Kora Entertainment\n| producer   = Lizer, Takis, Masterland, Placide\n| prev_title = Arrependimento\n| prev_year  = 2013\n| next_title = [[Addicted (Best Life Music album)|Addicted]]\n| next_year  = 2017\n| misc       = {{Singles\n | name        = Arrependimento II\n | type        = studio\n | single1     = Never Sleep\n | single1date = January 4, 2014\n}}\n}}\n'''''Arrependimento II''''' is the second studio album by Burundian group [[Best Life Music]], released by Kora Entertainment on September 11, 2016. The album's [[Record producer|production]] was handled by Lizer from Wasafi (WCB), Masterland, Placide and Takis. The 10-track album features guest appearances from Patient Matabaro, Blak G and Ashley Diva.\n\n==Track listing==\n{{Track listing\n| extra_column    = Producer(s)\n| total_length    = 67:41\n\n| title1          = Never Sleep\n| note1           = featuring Patient Matabaro\n| extra1          = Placide\n| length1         = 4:24\n\n| title2          = Better Than\n| note2           = \n| extra2          = ILogos\n| length2         = 4:04\n\n| title3          = Overdose <ref name=\"bongo5\">{{cite web|url=http://bongo5.com/new-video-best-life-music-burundi-overdose-08-2016/|website=bongo5.com|title=New Video: Best Life Music (Burundi) &#8211; Overdose &#8211; Bongo5.com|accessdate=2017-08-12}}</ref>\n| note3           = \n| extra3          = Placide \n| length3         = 4:19\n\n| title4          = Rayban\n| note4           = \n| extra4          = Placide\n| length4         = 4:22\n\n| title5          = Keep Swagg On\n| note5           = featurin