ashwe/|accessdate=15 September 2014|publisher=GLM Mix}}</ref>\n| Kent-P<ref>{{cite news|title=SATURA AMABAFLE yaraye ifashwe amasanamu.|url=http://umuravyo.com/?p=1182|accessdate=17 September 2014|publisher=Umuravyo}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Impemburo\"\n| rowspan=\"1\"| 2015\n| Kent-P\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Generation Moto Moto ft Nizzo Kaboss\"\n| rowspan=\"1\"| 2015\n| Gilbert Benjamins & Kent-P\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Nyampinga\"\n| rowspan=\"1\"| 2016\n| Gilbert Benjamins & Kent-P\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"African Girl\"\n| rowspan=\"1\"| 2016\n| Meddy Menz & Kent-P\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"I Love You ft [[Urban Boyz]]\"\n| rowspan=\"1\"| 2016\n| Grate Pest\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Too Much\"\n| rowspan=\"1\"| 2017\n| Kent-P\n|-\n! Scope=\"row\"| \"Ivyo Bintu Ft [[Producer Washington| Magic Washington]]\"\n| rowspan=\"1\"| 2017\n| Kent-P\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Feel Love\"\n| rowspan=\"1\"| 2017\n| Sasha Vybz\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"No Love\"\n| rowspan=\"1\"| 2018\n| Joowzey\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Karabarya\"\n| rowspan=\"1\"| 2018\n| Sasha Vybz\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"50-100 (Amabuno) ft [[Best Life Music]], Belle 9ice, [[Clementine Kavy]] and Bain Turo\"\n| rowspan=\"1\"| 2019\n| Kent-P\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Love Controller\"\n| rowspan=\"1\"| 2019\n| Taty Lameck\n{{end}}\n{{-}}\n\n====Featuring videos====\n* Katoto Rmx by Dj Pro ft Mkombozi<ref name=\"Katoto Rmx by Dj Pro ft Sat B & Mkombozi Official Video Music\">{{cite web|title=Katoto Rmx by Dj Pro ft Sat B & Mkombozi Official Video Music|url=http://isaacproduction.com/katoto-rmx-by-dj-pro-ft-sat-b-mkombozi-official-video-music/|website=http://isaacproduction.com|publisher=Isaac|accessdate=11 June 2014}}</ref>\n* Stay With Me by Alida B<ref>{{cite web|title=Stay With me \u2013 SAT B ft ALIDA (Official Video)|url=http://www.eastafricanhit.com/stay-sat-b-ft-alida-official-video/|website=http://www.eastafricanhit.com|publisher=East African Hit|accessdate=6 January 2014}}</ref>\n*\n\n==Awards==\n===[[Buja Music Awards]] ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Year\n!Prize\n!Work/Recipient\n!Result\n|-\n|2019\n|''Artist Of The Year''\n|\n|{{win}}\n|-\n|-\n|2019\n|''Song of the Year''\n|No Love\n|{{win}}\n|-\n|-\n|2019\n|''Best Performance''\n|\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|-\n|2019\n|''Best Male Artist''\n|\n|{{win}}\n|-\n|-\n|2019\n|''Video Of The Year''\n|Karabarya directed by Sasha Vybz\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|}\n\n{{-}}\n\n===Afrima===\n{{awards table}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\"|2016\n|Sat-B\n|Most Promising Artist\n|{{Nom}}\n|-\n{{end}}\n\n{{Infobox musician awards\n| name = Sat-B\n| image = \n| image_size = 220px\n| alt =\n| caption = \n| collapse = yes\n| wins = 8\n| nominations = 3\n\n| award1 =  Afrima\n| award1W = 0\n| award1N = 1\n| award2 =  Top Ten Music Awards\n| award2W = 1\n| award2N = 0\n| award3 = Radio Achievement\n| award3W = 3\n| award3N = 0\n| award4 = Ikoh Multiservice\n| award4W = 1\n| award4N = 0\n| award5 = [[Buja Music Awards]]\n| award5W = 3\n| award5N = 2\n}}\n\n===Ikoh Multiservice===\n{{awards table}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\"|2014\n|Sat-B\n|Artist of the Year<ref>{{cite news|title=Ikoh Awards|url=http://ubmnews.com/hamenyekanye-impanvu-ikomeye-yatumye-sat-b-yanka-kwakira-agashimwe-kadasanzwe-bari-bamuhaye-soma-ngaha-wunve/|accessdate=23 December 2014|publisher=UbmNews}}</ref>\n|{{Won}}\n|-\n{{end}}\n\n===Top Ten Tube Music Awards===\n{{awards table}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\"|2013\n|Ikinyamugigima<ref>{{cite news|title=AMASENGESHO YA SAT-B YARAYE YUMVIWE|url=http://indundi.com/news/page/33383|publisher=Indundi}}</ref>\n|Video of the Year<ref>{{cite news|title=REVUE: TOP TEN TUBE MUSIC AWARDS 2013|url=http://art-rhythm.blogspot.com/2013/09/revue-top-ten-tube-music-awards-2013.html|accessdate=6 September 2013|publisher=art-rhythm}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=\u00d4 joie !, les Top Ten Tube Music Awards remettent le couvert \u00e0 l\u2019IFB|url=http://www.iwacu-burundi.org/top-ten-tube-music-awards-musique-ifb/|accessdate=6 September 2013|publisher=Iwacu Burundi}}</ref>\n|{{Won}}\n|-\n{{end}}\n\n===Radio Achievement ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Year\n!Award Ceremony\n!Prize\n!Work/Recipient\n!Result\n|-\n|2017\n|Buja Fm Hits Connection\n|''Song of the month January''\n|Too Much\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|-\n|2017\n|RFM\n|''Artist of the Year''\n|Feel Love\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|-\n|2018\n|Buja Fm\n|''Song of the Year''\n|No Love\n|{{won}}\n|-\n\n|}\n\n{{-}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|2 }}\n\n==External links==\n* [https://www.facebook.com/pages/Sat-b-satlight/325080860937529?ref=hl Sat-B on Facebook]\n\n[[Category:1989 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Burundian singers]]\n", "text_old": "{{EngvarB|date=August 2014}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=August 2014}}\n{{Infobox musical artist\n| name             = Sat-B\n| image            = \n| image_size       = \n| landscape        = \n| alt              = \n| caption          = \n| background       = solo_singer\n| birth_name       = Bizimana Aboubakar Karume\n| alias            = Sat-B, Satura Amabafle\n| birth_date       = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1982|12|07}}\n| birth_place      = [[Bujumbura]], [[Burundi]]\n| genre            = [[Afro pop music|Afropop]], [[R&B]]\n| occupation       = [[singer-songwriter]], [[performer]]\n| instrument       = \n| years_active     = 2009\u2013present\n| label            = [[Empire Avenue (record label)|Empire Avenue]]\n| associated_acts  = {{flatlist|\n*Yoya\n*[[Tom Close]]\n*Fireman\n*Big Fizzo\n*[[Jean-Pierre Nimbona | Kidum]]\n*[[Urban Boyz]]\n*Frasha [[P-Unit]]\n*[[Miss Erica]]\n*[[Dully Sykes]]\n* [[Best Life Music]]\n*Belle 9ice\n*Aslay\n}}\n}}\n'''Bizimana Aboubakar Karume''' (born 7 December 1982), popularly known by his stage name '''SAT-B''', is an award winning Burundian recording artist, singer, songwriter, dancer and performer, Sat-B was born and bred Bujumbura city.\n\n==History==\nThe multi-talented Artiste started doing the local Hip Hop in the group Wanavesi Kikosi in his [[Kanyosha]] neighbourhood in [[Bujumbura]] city before launching his solo career in 2009.\nHe made his big break 2010 with the single \"Inkuru y'Ukuri\" and since then he has consistently delivered hit after hit to become one of biggest [[Burundi]]an stars in R & B and Hip Hop. Some of his popular songs include Satura Amabafle, Too Much, Feel Love and No Love.\nHe has been nominated in continental Awards, won various local awards, has been brand ambassador to varios multinational brands as well as collaborated with different artistes in the region including Yoya, Big Fizzo, Kidum, [[Sauti Sol]], Meddy among others.\nHe has previously toured [[Rwanda]] and [[Uganda]] in 2016 for Iwacu Album Launch with performances in Kigali and Kampala respectively.\nFollowing the success of his Hit \u201cFEEL LOVE\u201d in 2017, he has released yet another follow up HIT \u201cNO LOVE\u201d in 2018 which is already taking over the radio airwaves and clubs.\n\n==Discography==\n\n===Albums===\n*Inkuru y'Ukuri (2010)\n*[[IWACU]] (2016)\n\n===Singles===\n*\"Unkundiy'iki\" <ref>{{cite news|url=https://twitter.com/djGoz_/status/1098021021687328768?s=19|title=Unkundiy'iki by SAT B - Produced by Dj Goz|last=|first=|date=|work=|access-date=|publisher=dj Goz (Bizzy Beats)}}</ref>\n*\"Nyanzobe\" <ref>{{cite news|title=Nyanzobe cartonne , SAT B explique\u2026|url=http://akeza.net/?p=6946|publisher=Akeza}}</ref>\n*\"Reka Mbege\"\n*\"Simba Hawana Meno\"\n*\"Nyandika\"\n*\"Maisha\"\n*\"Akabeba\"\n*\"Walimwengu\"\n*\"Satura Amabafle\"\n*\"Wezere\"<small>(featuring Fizzo)</small> <ref>{{cite web|title=SAT-B FT FIZZO- WEZERE|url=http://africanmuzikmag.com/sat-b-ft-fizzo-wezere/|website=http://africanmuzikmag.com|publisher=African Muzik Magazine|accessdate=29 September 2014}}</ref>\n*\"Urankirigita featuring [[Urban Boyz]]\n*\"Kanitangaze\n* I Love You ft [[Urban Boyz]]\n*\"Rwagiye He?\n* \"ShimirImana\n*\"Ivyo Bintu ft [[Producer Washington|Magic Washington]]\n*\"Feel Love\"\n*\"No Love\"\n*\"Karabarya\"\n*\"50-100 (Amabuno)\" ft [[Best Life Music]], Belle 9ice, [