ne, Helena Taylor, Wendee Tomson, Kazue Yamamoto, and Akihito Yamashita.<ref name=\"AC-2005\">{{cite web | url = https://animecons.com/events/info/516/anime-expo-2005 | title = Anime Expo 2005 Information | publisher = AnimeCons.com | accessdate = 2018-06-25}}</ref>\n}}\n{{Convention list\n| date       = July 1\u20134, 2006\n| venue      = Anaheim Convention Center\n| location   = Anaheim, California\n| attendance = 40,647\n| guests     = [[Laura Bailey (voice actress)|Laura Bailey]], [[Clamp (manga artists)|CLAMP]], Crispin Freeman, [[T\u014dru Furuya|Toru Furuya]], Noboru Ishiguro, Yutaka Izubuchi, [[Koge-Donbo]], [[Tomoki Kyoda]], [[Mana (Japanese musician)|Mana]], [[Vic Mignogna]], [[Seiji Mizushima]], [[Hiroshi Nagahama]], Atsuko Nakajima, [[Mick Takeuchi]], and [[yozuca|yozuca*]].<ref name=\"AC-2006\">{{cite web | url = https://animecons.com/events/info/634/anime-expo-2006 | title = Anime Expo 2006 Information | publisher = AnimeCons.com | accessdate = 2018-06-25}}</ref>\n}}\n{{Convention list\n| date       = June 29\u2013July 2, 2007\n| venue      = Long Beach Convention Center\n| location   = Long Beach, California\n| attendance = 41,671\n| guests     = [[Tetsur\u014d Araki|Tetsuro Araki]], [[Michael Arias]], Greg Ayres, Laura Bailey, [[Steven Blum]], Johnny Yong Bosch, [[Minori Chihara]], [[Leah Clark]], Colleen Clinkenbeard, [[Justin Cook]], [[Caitlin Glass]], [[Y\u016bko Got\u014d|Yuko Goto]], Kate Higgins, [[Aya Hirano]], [[Y\u016bna Inamura|Yuuna Inamura]], Eisaku Inoue, [[Chiaki Ishikawa]], Taliesin Jaffe, Satoru Kannagi, Hideo Katsumata, [[Takaaki Kidani]], [[Masaru Kitao]], [[Mike McFarland]], [[Mary Elizabeth McGlynn]], [[Haruko Momoi|Halko Momoi]], Shuhei Morita, Hiroshi Nagahama, Sumire Nanohana, Tomonori Ochikoshi, [[Tony Oliver]], [[Oreskaband]], Kate Oxley, Takaharu Ozaki, [[Brina Palencia]], Orion Pitts, [[Brandon Potter]], [[Dai Sat\u014d|Dai Sato]], [[Savage Genius|savage genius]], [[Patrick Seitz]], [[Stephanie Sheh]], [[Anna Tsuchiya]], [[